metadata.name: Bad Bunny #1
metadata.description: What happens when a bad alien meets a devious rabbits? Laser fights, carrot binging, a whole lot of fun, and a little dash of mutations. Meet the joining of BAD and BTFD - a collection of 10,000 BAD Bunnies. With a heart for community, spicy chats, and ambitious teams - BAD Bunnies are here to kick Web3's butt!
